sequenceDiagram
    participant C as CLI
    participant A as API
    participant D as DB
    participant M as MinIO

    C->>C: Hash file
    C->>C: OPRF/mock -> file_key
    C->>C: HKDF -> enc_key, pow_seed
    C->>C: Ed25519 seed -> pk_pow, tag
    C->>A: POST /files/check
    A->>D: find file by tag
    D-->>A: exists or not exists

    alt tag exists
        A-->>C: exists=true
        C->>A: POST /files/challenge
        A->>D: store nonce and TTL
        A-->>C: nonce and context
        C->>C: sign(context,user_id,tag,nonce)
        C->>A: POST /files/claim
        A->>D: verify signature with pk_pow
        A->>D: insert user_files
        A-->>C: claimed
    else tag missing
        C->>C: AES-GCM encrypt file
        C->>A: POST /files/upload/init
        A->>D: create upload_session
        A-->>C: session_id and presigned PUT URL
        C->>M: PUT ciphertext
        C->>A: POST /files/upload/complete
        A->>M: stat object
        A->>D: create files row if absent
        A->>D: create user_files row
        A->>D: mark session completed
        A-->>C: file_id
    end
